 \mathopen {}\left \lparen D_0,F_0\right \rparen \mathclose {}
 to 
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen 
 \mathopen {}\left \lvert C\right \rvert \mathclose {}
, 1_{
 \mathopen {}\left \lvert C\right \rvert \mathclose {}
